Avoid the creation of unnecessary local variables
https://docs.pmd-code.org/pmd-doc-7.13.0/pmd_rules_java_codestyle.html#unnecessarylocalbeforereturn
```


public class Foo {
   public int foo() {
     int x = doSomething();
